{"tid":2147356,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黎巴嫩漠視10次警告  拒獨立查爆炸案","createTime":"2020-08-09T07:44:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-09T08:51:35.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"12c9bf7d373af666c82773672c71abd293837a8d","tid":2147356,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T07:44:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200809/6IN6KMJZMPJ24ZMABVSJTU765M/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200809%2F6IN6KMJZMPJ24ZMABVSJTU765M%2F&d=SXj%2FfRDdIS6Y9psqMYminHNo2vAooDXMO4YLrfRUzdI%3D&h=d880367c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200809%2F6IN6KMJZMPJ24ZMABVSJTU765M%2F&h=267fcb64\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200809/6IN6KMJZMPJ24ZMABVSJTU765M/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n黎巴嫩漠視10次警告 <br />\n拒獨立查爆炸案<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/SkwVdKVEbO8yL2sS5gDH9hoLeZE=/640x432/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ABNK4OTIAEOSBO53GGNMACAHME.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FSkwVdKVEbO8yL2sS5gDH9hoLeZE%3D%2F640x432%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FABNK4OTIAEOSBO53GGNMACAHME.jpg&h=f16b9b7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n民眾在貝魯特烈士廣場悼念爆炸死傷者。路透社<br />\n<br />\n黎巴嫩貝魯特上周爆炸、存有大量硝酸銨的港口倉庫，據報同時放了煙花，相信是調查爆炸起因的重要線索。另有文件顯示，黎巴嫩海關、軍方、安全機關和司法機構至少10次警告倉內硝酸銨有危險，然而毫無行動。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。，「裏面有3、40個尼龍袋的煙花」，又謂曾投訴倉庫不安全。據報確認有煙花在倉庫的不止謝哈迪一人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/HXIJDsFyeevqsICfh2kjrntFnAA=/640x359/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KTEBO6SHIHJ2H5VNJDY6DCZ5VQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FHXIJDsFyeevqsICfh2kjrntFnAA%3D%2F640x359%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKTEBO6SHIHJ2H5VNJDY6DCZ5VQ.jpg&h=ea740450&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n爆炸港口據報另存有大批煙花，現場仍一片狼藉。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/uB7-oMZZm9zvWwsDJ-f_uHZVZHQ=/190x126/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5HGXVNQHQEQPXZTZIOTD573NYE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FuB7-oMZZm9zvWwsDJ-f_uHZVZHQ%3D%2F190x126%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5HGXVNQHQEQPXZTZIOTD573NYE.jpg&h=d4603358&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n不少義工協助清理瓦礫。路透社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n港口倉庫另存大量煙花<br />\n<br />\n謝哈迪又稱從舊同事口中得知，12號倉庫冒煙前約半小時，有人以電動工具修理倉庫閘，「所以我相信這場工程引發了災難」。<br />\n<br />\n顯示黎巴嫩當局知道港口倉庫內。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n各國領袖、壓力團體和黎巴嫩人都要求為爆炸案展開獨立國際調查，但奧恩拒絕，指會模糊真相，又謂國內調查很快會令事件水落石出，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n不滿政府無能害死至少158人的貝魯特市民，昨日再度示威，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高官「落區」遭民眾趕走<br />\n<br />\n黎巴嫩教育部長馬傑祖卜和司法部長納札早前「落區」助義工清理瓦礫時被趕走，民眾大喊「辭職！」、「人民想政權倒台」、「人來！絞刑架」、「貪腐部長」等口號。<br />\n<br />\n法國和聯合國今日會主持國際援助視像會議，平常被批奉行保護主義的美國總統特朗普亦加入。聯合國世界糧食計劃署宣佈向受爆炸影響的家庭提供糧食，包括在爆炸中損失嚴重的小麥。<span class=\"orange\"><span class=\"large\">荷蘭外交部昨指駐黎巴嫩大使夫人亦在大爆炸傷重不治。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n英國《衞報》/法新社/美聯社"},{"pid":"6727e174d5d0cb0a9b38d3a1fc73f3f1bcfdf6bd","tid":2147356,"uid":273791,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T07:45:51.000Z","msg":"屌原來咁撚邪惡"},{"pid":"b6252b64c6e62eabfa18f0e25f70306c883e8c8a","tid":2147356,"uid":6192,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T07:48:34.000Z","msg":"黎巴嫩正苦係香港正苦d fd 黎"},{"pid":"9ac2c992e43e530aba8b5911c36058ab5ef3218b","tid":2147356,"uid":115847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-09T08:45:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5098c94f67c0a5aebd0d770fd8de